Description_lang: $@spelldesc435823The underground of Khaz Algar is filled with a menagerie of lifeforms, large and small, each with their own unique features and behaviors.One such lifeform is a species of magical spore, not too dissimilar from the ones found in Zaralek Cavern on the Dragon Isles. These spores, however, aren't as symbiotic.Gathering an herb that hosts these spores will grant some Viridescent Spores, but have also been noted to cause strange hallucinations. Proceed with caution.
